            "id": 6439448,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 伊魯米納(ILMN-US)大漲5.08%，報126.49美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>伊魯米納(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ILMN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ILMN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ILMN-US</a>)截至台北時間01日00:04股價上漲6.12美元，報126.49美元，漲幅5.08%，成交量583,660（股），盤中最高價126.50美元、最低價121.43美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+1.51%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.49%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.05%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.33%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>伊魯米納(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ILMN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ILMN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ILMN-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-7.76%</li> <li>近 1 月：+2.29%</li> <li>近 3 月：-19.59%</li> <li>近 6 月：+26.67%</li> <li>今年以來：-8.23%</li></ul></section></main>",
